<Base
  title="About SoloStack"
  description="How SoloStack tests AI and automation tools for one-person businesses."
>
  <h1>About SoloStack</h1>
  <p>
    SoloStack reviews the software that runs one-person businesses — funnel
    builders, email marketing, AI writing and automation tools. Our method:
    sign up (usually on the free plan, because that's where you'll start too),
    run the tool through a real task — an actual funnel, a real email sequence,
    genuine client work — and report what happened, including the failures and
    the paywalls.
  </p>
  <p>
    We don't promise income and we don't do hype. We tell you what a tool does,
    what it costs, and whether it earns a place in your stack.
  </p>
  <p>See how this site makes money on the <a href="/disclosure">disclosure page</a>.</p>
</Base>
